summary: This little mod adds a view new options for trophies to the Hearthfire homes (Trophy Room).
descriptionHtml:
Background

Unfortunaly my computer hasn't enough power to actually play Skyrim. Voice and image aren't synchron and already the
first 15 minutes need at least 20 in reality. I normally play on PS4 and
I just got the Legendary Edition to start modding, but now I can't test
my own mods myself. :(
So I hope for some brave tester and their feedback.

What is this mod about?

This little mod adds a few new options for trophies to the Hearthfire homes (Trophy Room).
Hope you like it.
author: Diilsoszaam
